<subSubSection pageId="24" pageNumber="968" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="24.[128,772,201,632]" pageId="24" pageNumber="968">
<emphasis box="[174,255,421,444]" italics="true" pageId="24" pageNumber="968">Note. –</emphasis>
On the same sheet a rather fragmentary second specimen is mounted, barcode K000583149 [image!]. Hooker did not mention flowers when he described the plant in 
<emphasis box="[158,382,513,537]" italics="true" pageId="24" pageNumber="968">Gardeners Chronicle</emphasis>
, so it is hard to judge if he just saw one of the specimens or both. We selected the more complete specimen as lectotype.
</paragraph>
